  "title": "Cloud Operations Lead",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Act as the primary customer contact for operational issues, ensuring timely resolution.</li><li>Coach and guide engineers to drive operational excellence.</li><li>Assign and manage team workloads to ensure efficient task delivery.</li><li>Oversee security operations, vulnerability management, and patching activities.</li><li>Proactively manage daily operations, incidents, and problem resolution.</li><li>Lead and participate in engagements with Cloud Service Providers, OEMs, and principals.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>5+ years of experience in an enterprise IT environment.</li><li>Strong understanding of ITSM frameworks (e.g. ITIL).</li><li>Knowledge of IT security and compliance standards.</li><li>Strong technical expertise in one or more areas: systems, networking, cybersecurity, BCP, AD & IAM, EUC.</li><li>Experience with enterprise tools (e.g. Tenable, CyberArk, NetBackup, Splunk, Palo Alto, Symantec).</li></ul><p>(EA Reg No: 20C0312)<br />Please email a copy of your detailed resume to <strong>qianyu@talentsis.com.sg</strong> for immediate processing.<br />Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
